TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT substr(se.level_data,4,10) OrgTPNumber, e.struc_lvl struc_lvl, e.struc_elm StrucElementNbr, se.opunit OperationalUnit, e.elm_name ElementName, se.ou_id AS org_node_id, se.product_id as product_id
FROM stg_param_winscr_tb stg,
stg_eiss_tb se, -- stg_test_roster str, org_node n, EISS_ORG_BC_TPE e
WHERE se.product_id = stg.product_id AND se.customer_id = stg.customer_id AND se.level_type = 'OU' AND n.org_node_id = se.ou_id AND n.org_node_code = e.org_node_code(+) AND e.org_node_code = e.parent_spcl_code AND se.customer_id= e.customer_id AND se.product_id = e.product_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT se.customer_id as customer_id, ns.org_node_name SchoolName, ns.org_node_id SchoolNo, ns.org_node_code SchoolCode, nc.org_node_name TeacherName, se.grade Grade, se.ou_id org_node_id, se.opunit opunit, se.st_id as item_set_id, se.gh_id as class_org_node_id, se.test_roster_id as test_roster_id, se.product_id as product_id
FROM STG_EISS_TB se, org_node ns, org_node nc
WHERE
level_type = 'ST' AND se.Sh_Id = ns.org_node_id AND se.gh_id = nc.org_node_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT tc.test_name as test_name, tc.commodity_code as commodity_code, nvl(tr.form_assignment,'B') as test_form, tc.eiss_test_level as eiss_test_level, tc.test_display_name as commodityCodeDesc, se.gh_id as teacher_org_node_id, s.grade as stu_grade, se.test_roster_id as test_roster_id FROM test_roster tr, test_admin ta, test_catalog tc, stg_param_winscr_tb stg, stg_eiss_tb se, student s
WHERE se.test_roster_id = tr.test_roster_id AND se.sr_id = s.student_id AND tr.test_admin_id = ta.test_admin_id AND ta.test_catalog_id = tc.test_catalog_id AND tr.customer_id = stg.customer_id AND tr.customer_id = ta.customer_id AND ta.product_id = tc.product_id AND ta.product_id = stg.product_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: teacher_org_node_id = class_org_node_id AND stu_grade = in_stu_grade AND test_roster_id = test_roster_id1
